  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611800/extras/IMG_1202.PNG?t=1770413419\" /></span><br>Ride 'n' Chill!<br><br>A stylistic little arcade high score chaser with a banging soundtrack.<br><br>Atmospherically rich, with simple to learn controls, the game lets you dive in immediately and experience a mechanistically frantic experience!<br><br>Take a minute to leave the world behind, and defeat the Gosts in the Machine…<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611800/extras/IMG_1200.PNG?t=1770413419\" /></span><br>- Nice Drifty Controls<br>- Level Unlocks<br>- High Scores<br>- Vehicle Unlocks<br>- Overdrive mechanic <br>- Skin & Trails<br>- Time rewind <br>- Challenges & Badges<br>- Simple Controls & Gameplay<br>- Easy to Pick-Up<br>- Controller Support",
